data.description: Enjoy these GREAT buyer incentives with an acceptable offer by December 30:  *Seller will pay HOA dues for 2024  *Washer, Dryer, & Refrigerator will convey  *1-Year Home warranty up to $825  *$3,500 closing costs if buyer uses our preferred lender  Welcome to this spacious and elegant 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom haven that effortlessly combines luxury and comfort! Situated in a serene and desirable neighborhood, this home offers the perfect blend of modern amenities and timeless charm. Step into a grand foyer that welcomes you into the heart of this home. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing an inviting space for entertaining. Kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry, a center island with a breakfast bar, and a spacious pantry. Five generously sized bedrooms ensure everyone in the household has their own retreat. The master suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, complete with a luxurious ensuite bathroom with a soaking garden tub, dual vanities, a separate shower, and a walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms offer ample space, natural light, and ample closet storage. Enjoy the large bonus room upstairs. 'Whole Home Internet Connected Generac Generator.' Enjoy walking trails and 7 lakes.
